{"tid":919661,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【平心而論】香港填詞人級數/範數","createTime":"2018-11-28T08:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T10:33:05.000Z","uid":104096,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b41c7083dfeeff3b6737078893204aabf5579cd4","tid":919661,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"S級：<span style=\"color: gold;\">夕爺</span><br />\nA級：<span style=\"color: pink;\">小克 周耀輝</span><br />\nB級：<span style=\"color: green;\">黃偉文</span><br />\nF級：<span style=\"color: red;\">陳詠謙</span><br />\n<br />\n夕爺級數最高唔洗講，範數係人生、哲學、愛情、社會咩都得，當之無愧<br />\n<br />\nA級兩位各有千秋，小克對宇宙時間空間、靈魂伴侶嘅作品非常出眾（例如張繼聰周國賢嗰堆）//周耀輝唔洗多講，由達明一派去到麥浚龍，真係好多神作，好多探討兩性關係嘅歌，有電影感覺、畫面豐富，求其抽兩首講：借火、騷靈情歌、今天只做一件事、結等<br />\n<br />\n黃偉文係勁但已經回晒塘，佢以前嘅作品非常出色：落花流水、破相、漩渦等等，但近幾年太多口水歌，相比前幾位真係差咗啲，未免範疇唔多主要集中講啲普普通通嘅情愛，不過近排真係差就算kay兩首新歌都係比較直接直白，可能呢種就係佢嘅風格同埋長處<br />\n<br />\n陳詠謙唔撚洗講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收皮啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c5322c81464721d021d8bbb56e5f3a2a39786d","tid":919661,"uid":162316,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:19:11.000Z","msg":"黃偉文差極都A啦"},{"pid":"5ea9b91f95647e9192ca8f014ceaae77573f081a","tid":919661,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"66c5322c81464721d021d8bbb56e5f3a2a39786d","tid":919661,"uid":162316,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:19:11.000Z","msg":"黃偉文差極都A啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"我認同佢係a，但如果講緊呢一刻，我覺得未必"},{"pid":"e3c7a3568fdf23f0725936693abf06d713be26c1","tid":919661,"uid":202995,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime